Parent PID = 5421
Child's PID = 5422
Parent waiting for child to finish...
Child Process started
Child PID  = 5422
Child's Parent PID = 5421
Child: Written entry to attendance.txt
Parent: Written entry to attendance.txt
Done! Check attendance.txt
```

